# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Argus Alert Ingress — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The Vector-based alert pipeline replaces the old Go service.
# Webhooks are received on :8080, transformed, and routed to sinks.
#
# Sinks:
#   - stdout (always enabled — writes structured JSON for container logs)
#   - S3 (enabled when S3_ALERTS_BUCKET is set)
#   - GCP PubSub (enabled when GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT is set)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── General ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VECTOR_LOG_LEVEL=debug

# ── S3 Archival (optional) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# S3_ALERTS_BUCKET=argus-alerts
# AWS_REGION=us-west-2
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=

# ── GCP PubSub (optional) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT=your-gcp-project
# PUBSUB_TOPIC=argus-alerts
# GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/credentials.json
